  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eIn Birmingham, Michigan, a northern suburban neighborhood of Detroit, a distinctive residence redefines the relationship between architecture, privacy, and display. Designed by \u003ca href=\"https://www.khanna-schultz.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKhanna Schultz\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e, the \u003ca href=\"https://www.khanna-schultz.com/house-in-michigan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHouse for a Collector\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e project caters to a collector with a passion for rare Porsches and fine bourbon, seamlessly integrating his prized possessions into the fabric of daily life.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568593\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568593\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-2-810x492.jpg\" alt=\"Aerial view of a modern building with a flat roof, surrounded by landscaped lawns and autumn trees. A car is parked on the street above the property.\" width=\"810\" height=\"492\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-2-810x492.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-2-800x486.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-2-768x467.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRather than conforming to the conventional approach of a monolithic suburban home, the architects fragmented the structure into a series of interconnected volumes, arranged symmetrically around a central courtyard. This design choice not only mitigates the visual dominance of a single large building but also fosters a dynamic interplay between indoor and outdoor spaces. The courtyard itself serves as a unique focal point, where automobiles and social spaces coexist in a fluid, open environment.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568594\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568594\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-3-810x563.jpg\" alt=\"Modern house with large windows and brown exterior, surrounded by trees with vibrant autumn foliage and a well-manicured lawn.\" width=\"810\" height=\"563\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-3-810x563.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-3-800x556.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-3-768x533.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-3.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568595\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568595\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-4-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern building with large, flat walls surrounded by trees with autumn foliage. A driveway leads to the entrance, and sunlight casts shadows on the ground.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-4-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-