mercial buildings. Where sections of this concrete shell have been removed, weathered steel cladding introduces a warm contrast, adding depth and texture. Inside, a carefully curated palette of blackened steel, polished concrete, unpainted plaster, and pre-finished wood reinforces the balance between refined luxury and raw utility.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568599\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568599\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-8-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with large windows, dark furniture, abstract artwork, and a decorative piano. Glass wall reveals a parked car in the adjacent area.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-8-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-8-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSustainability is woven into the project through strategic design and technological integration. A high-performance building envelope, triple-glazed windows, and a geothermal heating and cooling system work in unison to enhance energy efficiency, ensuring the home is as environmentally conscious as it is visually striking.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568600\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568600\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-9-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with large windows, dark grey sofas, a round table with red flowers, and a piano. Sunlight streams in illuminating autumn trees outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-9-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-9-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568601\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568601\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-10-810x1206.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior hallway with large windows on the left, black cabinetry on the right, and a sleek black counter with chairs in the foreground. Sunlight streams in, casting shadows on the floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1206\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-10-810x1206.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-10-800x1191.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-10-768x1143.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-10-1032x1536.jpg 1032w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568602\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568602\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-11-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen with large windows, black island countertop, wooden dining table, and views of trees and neighboring houses.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-11-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-11-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568603\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568603\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-12-810x546.jpg\" alt=\"Modern dining room with a wooden table, chairs, and a minimalist black kitchen. Large windows provide natural light. Artwork on wall, vase with branches on table. Greenery visible outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"546\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-12-810x546.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-12-800x539.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-12-768x518.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568604\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568604\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\