Detroit-Robert-Schultz-16-768x1174.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-16-1005x1536.jpg 1005w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568608\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568608\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-17-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist interior with two sets of stairs divided by a wall; one ascending on the left and the other descending on the right, both with soft lighting.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-17-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-17-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-17-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-17-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568609\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568609\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-18-810x549.jpg\" alt=\"Modern architectural interior with a narrow corridor featuring glass walls and a wooden floor, connecting two sections of a building. Horizontal beams are visible through the glass.\" width=\"810\" height=\"549\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-18-810x549.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-18-800x542.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-18-768x520.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInside, a monochromatic color palette and scaled back details lend toward the client’s wishes to feature their beloved objects, including the cars, curated furnishings and art, and the extensive whiskey collection. Unexpected details, like a floating bridge connecting the upper volumes and a hanging Jim Zivic hammock swing in the primary suite, add to the minimalist interior.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568610\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568610\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-19-810x533.jpg\" alt=\"Modern room with dark walls, a suspended sofa facing a large window with autumn trees visible outside, and a linear fireplace on the left wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-19-810x533.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-19-800x526.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-19-768x505.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-19-385x252.jpg 385w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568611\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568611\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-20-810x657.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist living room with gray sectional sofa, lounge chair, and large window showcasing autumn foliage. Neutral tones dominate with a dark rug and simple decor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"657\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-20-810x657.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-20-800x649.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-20-768x623.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568612\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568612\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-21-810x527.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with matte black fixtures, minimalist design, large mirror, towel on a hook, and a freestanding tub next to a floor-to-ceiling window with a view of trees.\" width=\"810\" height=\"527\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-21-810x527.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-21-800x520.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-21-768x499.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"h