3e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568615\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568615\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-24-810x1007.jpg\" alt=\"Modern building with large glass windows revealing a bright interior with chairs and a table. It\u0026#39;s adjacent to a lawn and a tree with autumn-colored leaves, set against a twilight sky.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1007\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-24-810x1007.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-24-800x994.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-24-768x955.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-24-1236x1536.jpg 1236w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-24.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=568616\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-568616\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-25-810x536.jpg\" alt=\"Modern two-story house with large glass windows, flat roof, and illuminated autumn trees on both sides, viewed from the street.\" width=\"810\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-25-810x536.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-25-800x529.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-25-768x508.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/House-for-a-Collector-Detroit-Robert-Schultz-25.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information on Khanna Schultz, visit \u003ca href=\"https://www.khanna-schultz.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003ekhanna-schultz.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mmoranphoto/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eMichael Moran\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n\u003cem\u003ePhotography styling by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/carinscheve/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eCarin Scheve\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
